item.title: Basic Data Analysis (in R)
item.description: Note: This piece is a quick view for data analysis,my experience of data analysis, and summary of R packages for water analysis. It might not cover everything, if you have more questions, other interests, or any suggestion, I welcome and appreciate. What is data analysis? Data analysis is a process of inspecting, cleansing, transforming, and modeling data with the goal of discovering useful information, informing conclusions, and supporting decision-making. - Wikipedia
